                <persName type="authority">Aditya Bahadur Dinha, Mahārāja</persName>
              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīmatparamahaṃsaparivrājakācāryākhaṃḍānusmṛtipūjyapādaśiṣyeṇākhaṃḍādamunināviracite vivaraṇatatvadīpane tṛtīpasūtraṃ samāptaṃm // śubham astu // (f. 10v).</colophon>
